data.body:
**The shipped GamePlugin.h in Blank Project gives following errors in build process:**
Error C2039 'SetExtensionId': is not a member of 'CMyClass' (GamePlugin.h 58)
Error C2039 'GetGameObjectExtensionRMIData': is not a member of 'CMyClass' (GamePlugin.h 45)


**GamePlugin.h** in **Blank Project** has the following GetGameObjectExtensionRMIData function:
```c++
void GetGameObjectExtensionRMIData(void** ppRMI, size_t* nCount)
{
	T::GetGameObjectExtensionRMIData(ppRMI, nCount);
}
```
But instead, it must be implemented in following way, which shipped with other examples:
```c++
void GetGameObjectExtensionRMIData(void** ppRMI, size_t* nCount)
{
	*ppRMI = nullptr;
	*nCount = 0;
}
```

**GamePlugin.h** in **Blank Project** has the following RegisterEntityWithDefaultComponent function:
```c++
template<class T>
static void RegisterEntityWithDefaultComponent(const char *name)
{
IEntityClassRegistry::SEntityClassDesc clsDesc;
	clsDesc.sName = name;

	static CObjectCreator<T> _creator;

	gEnv->pGameFramework->GetIGameObjectSystem()->RegisterExtension(name, &_creator, &clsDesc);
	T::SetExtensionId(gEnv->pGameFramework->GetIGameObjectSystem()->GetID(name));
}
```
But instead, it must be implemented in following way, which shipped with other examples:
```c++
template<class T>
static void RegisterEntityWithDefaultComponent(const char *name)
{
IEntityClassRegistry::SEntityClassDesc clsDesc;
	clsDesc.sName = name;

	static CObjectCreator<T> _creator;

	gEnv->pGameFramework->GetIGameObjectSystem()->RegisterExtension(name, &_creator, &clsDesc);
}
```
